OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772655073
OL,3,CMan who died after stabbing in
OL,4,CBirmingham named by police
OL,6,FA man who died after being stabbed in
OL,7,FAlum Rock in Birmingham, has been
OL,8,Fnamed as Ali Alshmari.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police were called to
OL,11,FBridge Road just after noon on
OL,12,FTuesday, March 3.
OL,14,FMr Alshmari who was 30, was pronounced
OL,15,Fdead at the scene a short time later.
OL,17,FA man aged 32 was arrested nearby and
OL,18,Fremains in custody on suspicion of
OL,19,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
