CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772655073
OL,3,CMan who died after stabbing in
OL,4,CBirmingham named by police
OL,6,FA woman in her 50s who suffered
OL,7,Finjuries to her hand, has since been
OL,8,Fdischarged from hospital.
OL,10,FUniformed and plain-clothed firearms
OL,11,Fofficers were at the scene,
OL,13,FThe incident is not being treated as
OL,14,Fterrorism-related.
OL,16,F"A tragic and violent attack"
OL,18,FPolice say officers are meeting with
OL,19,Fmembers of the community today, to
OL,20,Fdiscuss their concerns and offer
OL,21,Freassurances.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
