OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772655073
OL,3,CMan who died after stabbing in
OL,4,CBirmingham named by police
OL,6,FDet Supt James Munro from the Homicide
OL,7,Fdepartment said:
OL,9,F"This is a tragic and violent attack
OL,10,Fwhich has cost the life of Mr Alshmari
OL,11,Fand left a woman injured.
OL,13,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,14,Festablish exactly what happened and
OL,15,Fwhy, and the public's response has
OL,16,Fbeen fantastic.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
