OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1772655073
OL,3,CMan who died after stabbing in
OL,4,CBirmingham named by police
OL,6,F"We've had CCTV, dashcam and mobile
OL,7,Ffootage shared with us, which has been
OL,8,Fvery helpful for the investigation,
OL,9,Fand I'd urge anyone who's not yet been
OL,10,Fin touch with us to do so as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,F"We understand how deeply distressing
OL,14,Fand concerning this incident is and we
OL,15,Fwill have extra officers in the area
OL,16,Fto offer reassurance to the community."
